##############################
ABOUT
##############################

This project is an OpenSource substitute for Puma and Lince software.
This software was made for generate scenarios with some events that can occurs when you are planning some strategies.
The Grumbach Method is a good way for planning your enterprise strategies.

##############################
Installation
##############################

-The code now is using Perl 5.12 and vi editor, but everything can be changed. Linux distributions come with this softwares outofbox.
-Need create folders 'sistema','diagnostico' and 'visao' to work.

